title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VIII - Cascais
description:
World Update VIII was released late last week and has the focus on Portugal and Spain. In this video we will fly over Cascais which is a city close to Lisbon. We are departing from an airport close to the city and fly have a look at the photogrammetry content which has been applied to the city as part of World Update VIII
